CAN ACTUALLY SOUND
RATHER FLAT SOMETIMES.

243
00:14:16,500 --> 00:14:18,041
OF COURSE THERE ARE
VARYING DEGREES,

244
00:14:18,125 --> 00:14:19,708
BUT YOU'RE THE ONLY ONE
ABLE TO BRING OUT

