00:14:23,125 --> 00:14:25,041
THE AUDIENCE SHOUTS
WITH APPRECIATION. 

248
00:14:25,125 --> 00:14:27,708
THE ACKNOWLEDGMENT
OF A SPLENDID PERFORMANCE.

249
00:14:27,791 --> 00:14:30,166
- WHY DIDN'T YOU FINISH ME OFF?

250
00:14:30,250 --> 00:14:31,791
WHAT ARE YOU WAITING FOR?
IT'S OBVIOUS YOU COULD HAVE

251
00:14:31,875 --> 00:14:33,166
TAKEN ME OUT BY NOW.

252
00:14:33,250 --> 00:14:34,708
- THE ANSWER'S SIMPLE.

253
00:14:34,791 --> 00:14:37,416
