261
00:14:51,500 --> 00:14:53,166
- HELP ME, I--

262
00:14:53,250 --> 00:14:55,083
I CAN'T STOP MYSELF!

263
00:14:55,166 --> 00:14:58,416
OH, NO!
WHAT'S HAPPENING TO ME?!

264
00:14:58,500 --> 00:15:00,666
- LEGATO AGAIN.

265
00:15:00,750 --> 00:15:01,916
- HMM!

266
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:02,916
- ( saxophone playing )
- NO!

267
00:15:10,375 --> 00:15:12,250
- NO, PLEASE!

268
00:15:12,333 --> 00:15:15,166
PLEASE DON'T KILL ME.

269
00:15:18,666 --> 00:15:21,083
- AAH!

270
00:15:21,166 --> 00:15:24,083
- SOMEBODY HELP STOP ME!
PLEASE!

271
00:15:24,166 --> 00:15:26,791
HELP ME!

272
00:15:26,875 --> 00:15:28,250
- ( panting )

273
00:15:31,625 --> 00:15:33,500
AAH!

274
00:15:43,125 --> 00:15:46,541
WELL, THAT'S IT. NOW I NEED TO
SPEND A LITTLE TIME ALONE, OKAY?

275
00:15:48,708 --> 00:15:49,625
- ( animal bellows )

276
00:15:49,708 --> 00:15:51,041
- DON'T START BROODING, MERYL.

277
00:15:51,125 --> 00:15:52,625
IT'S A WASTE OF TIME AND ENERGY.

278
00:15:52,708 --> 00:15:54,291
