YOU'LL REGRET IT LATER,

279
00:15:54,375 --> 00:15:55,500
SO JUST STOP.

280
00:15:57,166 --> 00:15:58,083
- YOU'RE RIGHT,
YOU'RE RIGHT.

281
00:15:58,166 --> 00:15:59,291
YOU'RE ABSOLUTELY RIGHT.

282
00:15:59,375 --> 00:16:00,791
THIS IS NO TIME
TO LOSE MY NERVE.

283
00:16:00,875 --> 00:16:02,750
GOTTA KEEP GOING, RIGHT?
MERYL?

284
00:16:02,833 --> 00:16:04,375
LET'S GO!

285
00:16:04,458 --> 00:16:07,083
- ( grunts, groans )

286
00:16:07,166 --> 00:16:09,750
- ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

287
00:16:09,833 --> 00:16:12,791
