00:16:19,041 --> 00:16:21,958
- TALK ABOUT IRON WILL.

291
00:16:22,041 --> 00:16:23,291
- ( groans )

292
00:16:23,375 --> 00:16:25,500
- YOUR DEDICATION IS
COMMENDABLE.

293
00:16:29,208 --> 00:16:32,833
