00:16:33,916 --> 00:16:35,541
- STOP IT!

296
00:16:38,125 --> 00:16:39,583
- YOU GOTTA BE COOL.

297
00:16:46,875 --> 00:16:48,625
- AAH.

298
00:16:48,708 --> 00:16:49,750
- ( air hisses )

299
00:16:49,833 --> 00:16:50,916
- DAMN!

300
00:16:51,000 --> 00:16:52,291
MY "B"-FLAT!

301
00:16:52,375 --> 00:16:54,250
MY "B"-FLAT'S GONE!

302
00:16:54,333 --> 00:16:56,750
- SORRY, THE SHOW'S OVER.

303
00:16:56,833 --> 00:16:57,916
- WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

304
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,916
YOU BEEN TRYING
FOR A RICOCHET SHOT?

305
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:01,416
( chuckles )

306
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:04,208
MAYBE, BUT IT'S NOT QUITE TIME
FOR THE CURTAIN CALL YET.

307
00:17:04,291 --> 00:17:05,166
HA.

308
00:17:09,291 --> 00:17:11,875
I HAVE TO ACCEPT THIS
AS MY FATE.

309
00:17:11,958 --> 00:17:13,708
THE DESTINY
OF THE DYING.

310
00:17:13,791 --> 00:17:14,791
