00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:03,750
THAT IS WHY I MUST...

322
00:18:03,833 --> 00:18:05,083
I MUST END IT.

323
00:18:06,708 --> 00:18:07,875
END IT NOW.

324
00:18:09,500 --> 00:18:10,750
THIS IS THE CLIMAX,

325
00:18:10,833 --> 00:18:11,916
VASH THE STAMP--

326
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:12,916
- ( gunshot )

327
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:14,875
- ( breathing heavily )

328
00:18:23,166 --> 00:18:24,916
- SO DO YOU HATE ME?

329
00:18:26,833 --> 00:18:28,250
I'M NOT SURPRISED.

330
00:18:28,333 --> 00:18:29,750
IF YOU DO,
I WOULDN'T BLAME YOU.

331
00:18:29,833 --> 00:18:31,750
SO MANY SAD THINGS
HAPPENED TO YOU.

332
00:18:31,833 --> 00:18:34,083
WHETHER THEY ARE FRIEND
OR ENEMY,

333
00:18:34,166 --> 00:18:36,750
THE PEOPLE YOU MEET DIE.

334
00:18:36,833 --> 00:18:39,250
IT'S ENOUGH
TO SAP ONE'S TEARS.

335
00:18:39,333 --> 00:18:41,250
- SHUT UP!

336
00:18:41,333 --> 00:18:43,708
- YOU KNOW, THIS IS NOT
FINISHED YET.

337
00:18:43,791 --> 00:18:46,875
DID YOU REALLY EXPECT THE END
TO COME SO EASILY?

338
00:18:48,791 --> 00:18:50,750
DON'T YOU UNDERSTAND
YOU'RE NOT HUMAN?

339
00:18:50,833 --> 00:18:53,875
IT IS TIME TO REALIZE
EXACTLY WHO YOU ARE. 

340
00:18:57,250 --> 00:18:59,916
- NO.
PLEASE, IT CAN'T BE.

341
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:01,458
- THERE'S POWER IN THAT LIGHT.

342
00:19:01,541 --> 00:19:03,791
POWER THAT YOU HAVE
ALWAYS POSSESSED.

343
00:19:03,875 --> 00:19:06,625
EVEN MORE, THIS REPRESENTS
WHAT YOU ARE.

344
00:19:08,333 --> 00:19:09,708
- AAH.
( grunts )

345
00:19:09,791 --> 00:19:11,666
AAH!

346
00:19:17,041 --> 00:19:18,291
I-- I CAN'T--

347
00:19:19,375 --> 00:19:21,500
NOT AGAIN.

348
00:19:21,583 --> 00:19:24,333
NOT AGAIN!

349
00:19:27,375 --> 00:19:29,375
( breathing heavily )

350
00:19:29,458 --> 00:19:31,458
- HAVEN'T YOU GIVEN UP
YET, VASH?

351
00:19:31,541 --> 00:19:33,458
IT'S REALLY QUITE ANNOYING.

352
00:19:33,541 --> 00:19:34,750
- ( gunshot )
- AAH.

353
00:19:34,833 --> 00:19:36,583
( groans )

354
00:19:40,500 --> 00:19:41,416
BASTARD.

355
00:19:41,500 --> 00:19:42,750
- YOU'RE OUT OF OPTIONS.

356
00:19:42,833 --> 00:19:44,541
FIGHT BACK OR YOU'LL DIE.

357
00:19:44,625 --> 00:19:45,541
- ( gunshot )

358
00:19:45,625 --> 00:19:46,500
- ( groans )

359
00:19:48,958 --> 00:19:49,875
- ( softly chuckles )

360
00:19:49,958 --> 00:19:51,208
WHY DON'T YOU GO AHEAD?

361
00:19:51,291 --> 00:19:53,416
I WOULD WELCOME THIS
TO BE MY TIME.

362
00:19:53,500 --> 00:19:55,583
AFTER ALL, THERE'S NO REASON
FOR SUCH AN EGOCENTRIC,

363
00:19:55,666 --> 00:19:56,791
INCOMPLETE LIFE

364
00:19:56,875 --> 00:19:59,041
LIKE MINE TO BE ALLOWED
TO CONTINUE ANYWAY.

365
00:19:59,125 --> 00:20:01,375
GIVE ME THE GIFT OF NOTHINGNESS.

366
00:20:01,458 --> 00:20:03,041
GIVE ME DEATH.

367
00:20:03,125 --> 00:20:05,291
MY MASTER IS WAITING FOR YOU.

368
00:20:05,375 --> 00:20:08,458
HE'S LOOKING FORWARD
TO YOUR VISIT.

369
00:20:08,541 --> 00:20:11,041
I WAS COMPELLED
TO ATTACH THIS ARM TO MYSELF.

370
00:20:11,125 --> 00:20:13,916
I HAD TO, BECAUSE YOU
REFUSED TO BE BY HIS SIDE.

371
00:20:14,000 --> 00:20:16,625
- ( grunts )

372
00:20:16,708 --> 00:20:18,500
- KILL ME.

373
00:20:18,583 --> 00:20:19,958
- I CAN'T.

374
00:20:20,041 --> 00:20:21,708
- GO AHEAD.

375
00:20:21,791 --> 00:20:23,416
- I CAN'T!

376
00:20:24,666 --> 00:20:26,083
- ( woman panting )

377
00:20:26,166 --> 00:20:27,083
- ( gasps )
- ( grunts )

378
00:20:27,166 --> 00:20:28,625
- MILLY!

379
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:32,291
- ( thuds )
- ( both groaning )

380
00:20:32,375 --> 00:20:35,458
- STOP THEM.
NO MORE!

381
00:20:37,166 --> 00:20:38,208
- Both:
AAH!

382
00:20:39,375 --> 00:20:40,833
- I SAID STOP IT NOW!

383
00:20:40,916 --> 00:20:42,833
- THEN SHOOT ME!

384
00:20:49,291 --> 00:20:51,541
IT'S ALL RIGHT.
KILL ME.

385
00:20:51,625 --> 00:20:52,708
IT'S SIMPLE.

386
00:20:52,791 --> 00:20:54,500
ALL YOU NEED DO IS
PULL THE TRIGGER.

387
00:20:54,583 --> 00:20:56,041
ONCE YOU HAVE KILLED ME,

388
00:20:56,125 --> 00:20:57,625
THIS WILL ALL BE OVER.

389
00:20:57,708 --> 00:20:59,916
COME ON,
TIME TO CHOOSE.

390
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:01,625
YOU HAVE FREE WILL.

391
00:21:01,708 --> 00:21:03,416
- STOP IT.
DON'T MAKE ME SHOOT.

392
00:21:03,500 --> 00:21:05,125
- Milly and Meryl:
NO!

393
00:21:05,208 --> 00:21:07,375
- Milly:
NO, PLEASE!

394
00:21:07,458 --> 00:21:08,833
( whimpering )

395
00:21:08,916 --> 00:21:11,208
- YOUR FAITH IS
HOPELESSLY OBSTINATE.

396
00:21:11,291 --> 00:21:13,416
TO ACTUALLY BELIEVE
THE PRATTLINGS OF A WOMAN

397
00:21:13,500 --> 00:21:15,916
WHO SPEAKS IN IDEALISTIC TERMS
THAT ARE WORTHLESS.

398
00:21:16,000 --> 00:21:17,791
- ( gasps )
- I GUESS THAT KIND OF THINKING

399
00:21:17,875 --> 00:21:19,375
IS REASONABLE FOR
SOMEONE WHO'S LIVED

400
00:21:19,458 --> 00:21:20,666
FOR MORE THAN A CENTURY.

401
00:21:20,750 --> 00:21:23,666
BUT THAT--
THAT WAY OF LIFE IS PATHETIC.

402
00:21:23,750 --> 00:21:26,458
EVEN COMICAL.

403
00:21:26,541 --> 00:21:27,875
REM SAVEREM.

404
00:21:27,958 --> 00:21:29,833
( chuckles )
A WASTED EXISTENCE

405
00:21:29,916 --> 00:21:32,208
WHO ONLY SPOKE
IN AGGRAVATING LOGIC.

406
00:21:32,291 --> 00:21:34,375
A WORTHLESS HUMAN BEING...

407
00:21:34,458 --> 00:21:36,083
JUST LIKE ME.

408
00:21:36,166 --> 00:21:37,625
BUT UNLIKE YOU.

409
00:21:37,708 --> 00:21:38,708
- THAT'S ENOUGH!

410
00:21:41,333 --> 00:21:42,416
- Wolfwood's voice: 
LUCK AND PERSISTENCE

411
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:44,916
WON'T WORK FOREVER.

412
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:46,541
- ( gunshot )

413
00:21:46,625 --> 00:21:48,458
- Rem's voice: AS WE JOURNEY
THROUGH OUR LIVES,

414
00:21:48,541 --> 00:21:51,958
WE MUST ALWAYS SEARCH FOR WAYS
