415
00:21:54,125 --> 00:21:55,750
- ( girls groaning )

416
00:21:55,833 --> 00:21:57,375
- Wolfwood's voice: DON'T FORCE
YOUR WAY OF LIFE UPON OTHERS.

417
00:21:57,458 --> 00:21:58,833
- Rem's voice:
NO ONE HAS THE RIGHT

418
00:21:58,916 --> 00:22:01,625
TO TAKE THE LIFE OF ANOTHER.

