00:22:01,708 --> 00:22:03,125
- Wolfwood's voice:
DON'T TELL ME YOUR DREAMS

420
00:22:03,208 --> 00:22:05,083
IN A WORLD LIKE THIS.

421
00:22:05,166 --> 00:22:08,541
