422
00:22:08,625 --> 00:22:10,125
- Girls:
PLEASE, NO!

423
00:22:10,208 --> 00:22:11,333
- ( gasps )

424
00:22:27,500 --> 00:22:30,083
- Legato:
I UNDERSTAND...

425
00:22:30,166 --> 00:22:31,250
MASTER.

426
00:22:31,333 --> 00:22:33,416
VASH THE STAMPEDE
WILL EXPERIENCE

427
00:22:33,500 --> 00:22:36,375
ETERNAL PAIN AND SUFFERING.

428
00:22:37,791 --> 00:22:39,541
- ( laughing )

429
00:22:39,625 --> 00:22:42,208
( maniacal laughter )

430
00:22:42,291 --> 00:22:44,166
- ( end theme playing )

