00:22:51,125 --> 00:22:54,333
- ( singing in Japanese )

432
00:24:14,458 --> 00:24:16,250
- Vash:
I WAS DREAMING, REM.

433
00:24:16,333 --> 00:24:19,291
EVERYTHING WAS SO HORRIBLY DRY.

434
00:24:19,375 --> 00:24:20,250
THEY'RE ON THAT PLANET.

435
00:24:20,333 --> 00:24:23,583
EVEN PEOPLE'S HEARTS.

436
00:24:23,666 --> 00:24:26,833
AS I WATCHED THE PEOPLE
