437
00:24:26,916 --> 00:24:29,500
I KEPT WONDERING
WHY THEY WENT ON LIVING...

438
00:24:29,583 --> 00:24:31,250
HOW THEY KEPT ON LIVING.

439
00:24:31,333 --> 00:24:35,083
REM, LISTEN TO ME, REM...

440
00:24:35,166 --> 00:24:37,583
I DID A BAD THING.

